fields.name: IE (Ireland) - Agriculture Department
fields.comments:
1. Go to http://www.agriculture.gov.ie/agri-foodindustry/euinternationalpolicy/commonagriculturalpolicycap/capbeneficiariesdatabase/paymentsdatabase/cap_ben_master.jsp, accept terms
2.Open http://www.agriculture.gov.ie/capben/cap_ben_terms.jsp page in new tab (or reload)
3. Go to year, do one first search, use cookie for scraping
4. Scrape per Location by manually inserting the Locations into the POST form data of the Request Page Type
    AND adopt region for ScraperElem manually on every region change
5. Divide viewing results by 15 (entries per page) and adopt the range function for pagination
6. Start scraping (move every scraper JSON file to a separate file for later concatenation!)

GENERAL: Extremely short session period (< 15 min), start scraping process instantly!!!
